metadata.name: Confess
metadata.description:
The shadow that I see far away, the things I don't have and the things I don't realize.
It just swings in the distance, I can see it.
Such a distance that I can see, but I cannot tell whether it is approaching or passing. 
Is it too late if I invite it in? 
Yes, I am the one who opened the door. 
So, if I hadn't opened the door and looked, would they still be there? 
Would they still exist even if I didn't think about it or not realize it?
